title: World Toad in the Hole Championships grace English town of Lewes
text:
World Toad in the Hole Championships grace English town of Lewes 3:06pm BST - 02:22 
Aim of the traditional pub game originating from France is to land as many large brass coins or 'toads' in a table's small hole. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
